fields.name: Super Antiox
fields.description: Enjoy refreshing pomegranate-blueberry white tea taste while kicking butt of free radicals and pollutants. This antiox-rich tea is a blend of premium white teas, pomegranate, blueberry, sage and astralgulus—a powerful immune system booster.

fields.name: Green Energy
fields.description: A dynamite tea that delivers a citrus-fresh, stimulating cup with serious horsepower. Sweet, lightly citrus flavored, mellow yet invigorating blend of green tea, goji berries, ashwagandha "Indian Ginseng", chinese ginseng, licorice root and citrus.

fields.name: Deep Sleep
fields.description: This potent mix of herbs is bound to help send you to la-la land while tasting like a dream. Chamomile, rosehips, lavender, pink peppercorn, valerian, honeybush and kava kava is blended to be potent, complex and deeply delicious. Nighty night.

fields.name: Beauty
fields.description: Keep that schoolkid glow with a tea designed to enhance and protect the beauty in you. Tulsi herb said to improve resistance to toxins and pollutants, is blended with peppermint, ginger, and rosemary providing essential nutrients and tingly fresh taste.

fields.name: Mentalitea
fields.description: Help clear the cobwebs with a tea designed to perk up your peepers. China meets India traditions in this slightly sweet and savory blend of green tea, ginkgo, ginseng, coriander, fennel and licorice to provide a refreshing cup with a cool mental kick.

fields.name: Relief
fields.description: Colds and allergies suck. Your tea doesn’t have to with tea blended to make your symptoms more bearable. Lemongrass, rosehips, ginger, citrus, licorice root, sage, peppermint and cloves for a shot of vitamin C and a blast of deep mentholated relief.

fields.name: Digestive
fields.description: Make your belly better with this vanilla mint tea designed for unsettled tummies. A soothing, powerful blend of several digestives in one, this peppermint, anise, fennel, ginger, licorice, vanilla and calendula is intensely soothing and immensely delicious.

fields.name: Slim Balance
fields.description: Toasty orange spice soothes with this blend of ingredients said to boost to your metabolism. Oolong tea is known by some as a "slimming" tea and is mixed with cinnamon, citrus and rosehips—however much it burns those calories, it's darn tasty.

fields.name: Detox
fields.description: Feeling a little gritty? Cleanse with nutrient rich rooibos tea, peppercorn, fennel, coriander, hibiscus, ginger, licorice, schizandra berries, orange peel, milk thistle and basil. Antioxidant rich tea with detoxifying herbs and spices brew sweet savory taste.

fields.name: Hangover
fields.description: Forget the hair of the dog that bit you. Rejuvenate with this blend of yerba mate, mint, ginger, feverfew, dandelion, licorice, orange, cumin, myrrh, barberry and ginseng. Cleansing, settling and invigorating, designed to soothe mind and body.

fields.name: Raspberry Luxe
fields.description: Indulge in white tea leaves infused with delicate aromas and flavors of summer berries kissed with cocoa. Light, fruity,

fields.name: Blue Hawaii
fields.description: Take a dive into a cup of pure paradise with antioxidant-rich white tea swimming with real organic coconut and vanilla bits. A sinfully good blend of white teas, coconut, natural essences, vanilla pieces and blue cornflowers. It's aloha in your cup.

fields.name: Morning Rain
fields.description: Delight in a mellow cup bearing hints of sliced melon reminiscent of a fresh rain. A special blend of white tea, fresh cantaloupe essence and jasmine brews a refreshing clean cup with fresh flowery melon taste. Hot or over ice, let it rain, let it rain.

fields.name: Love Buds
fields.description: Whether you’re love sick or sick of love, this tea can be your heart’s desire. Soothe and refresh with a luscious blend of flower scented white teas, roses, lavender and peppermint. Floral, fresh, delicate and delightful, it's a white tea that's easy to love.

fields.name: Goji Bloom
fields.description: Find inner peace inside a refreshing, clean cup that has a citrus fresh taste and is as comforting and crisp as summer morning dew. An artful blend of white tea, nutrient rich goji berries, lemon myrtle, and flower blossoms for a delicate citrus taste.

fields.name: Harmony
fields.description: Beautiful, floral and fruitful, this blend is a potpourri of white tea deliciousness. White tea leaves are blended with a bounty of apple and mango fruits, flower blossoms, cinnamon and almonds infusing

fields.name: Peach n Peony
fields.description: Here’s a tea that’s bound to make life a bit peachier. White peony tea rich with antioxidants and nutty flavor blended with natural peach essences and aromatic blossoms. Light fruity notes with delicate white tea creates a refreshing uplifting cup.

fields.name: White Chai
fields.description: Low-caff antiox-rich white tea blended with classic Indian spices result in a mellow, spiced brew that's subtle and welcoming. White tea, cinnamon, ginger, cardamom, cloves, natural vanilla essences and flower blossoms that's subtle and spiced.

fields.name: White Peony
fields.description: Classic “Bia Mu Dan” white Peony from China. Antioxidant loaded, this white tea brews a delicate, herbaceous aroma with smooth body and slightly light, nutty taste that's more delicious from one infusion to the next. Low caff and highly delicious.

fields.name: Silver Needle
fields.description: Pure “Yin Zhen” Silver Needle white tea from China. Beautiful, subtle, prized tea that produces a light golden cup with woodsy body, savory aroma and delicate honeysuckle sweetness. It's handpicked, hand dried, one of the finest of pure teas.

fields.name: Green Coconut
fields.description: A little nutty, a little naughty and a lot nice. Get the luscious taste of fresh steamed green tea kissed with exotic coconut. Antioxidant rich good-for-you green tea is steamed maintaining rich nutrients and fresh taste then blended with coconut for a sweet creamy taste and simple soothing cup. Makes seriously good

fields.name: Paradise
fields.description: Fresh sencha green tea bursting with sweet tropical taste. Refresh and restore with a lush and intoxicating blend of Japanese green tea, pineapple pieces, natural tropical essences and flowers in a perfectly pleasurable cup. We'll see you in paradise. Makes great

fields.name: Orange Krush
fields.description: Creamsicles envy this green tea. Chill out with this perfectly smooth citrusy-vanilla green tea goodness that's simply divine both warm and

fields.name: Jasmine Blue
fields.description: If you thought jasmine green tea couldn’t get any better, it just did. Bold jasmine tea infused with flower petals and succulent antiox-rich blueberries. The floral sweetness of jasmine fuses perfectly with fruity blueberry for a fresh, fruity and fragrant taste.

fields.name: Roasted La Crème
fields.description: Take a toasty twist on green tea with roasted green tea combined with white chocolate bits creating a toasty, marshmallow-hazelnut flavor. Contains roasted green tea, natural vanilla essences and vanilla white chocolate green tea decadence.

fields.name: Mo Rockin Mint
fields.description: Classic "Moroccan Mint" kicked up a notch with extra bold peppermint freshness in this cooling blend of strong “gunpowder” green tea, peppermint and spearmint leaves. Especially soothing hot and refreshing over ice, this classic combo is done just right.

fields.name: Strawberry Sunrise
fields.description: Sip summer berries all year long with a blend designed to send your senses to a smooth strawberry nirvana. Steamed green tea with strawberry piece, rosehips, fruit essences and papaya pieces are fused as one for a sexy strawberry sensation.

fields.name: Mango Mist
fields.description: Get lost in the aromas of robust green tea soaring with soothing sweet mango ginger flavor. Select teas from India and China are blended with spices and fruits designed as amazing iced tea and scrumptious hot. Green tea, mango, ginger root, fennel seed and calendula brew intoxicating aroma and lingering fruity flavor.

fields.name: Earl Jazz
fields.description: Go green with this fresh take on classic Earl Grey taste. Smooth and light citrus flavor burst from this blend of robust green tea, citrus, jasmine and natural bergamot essence. If you are looking for a twist on a classic taste, you should like this take.

fields.name: Jasmine Pearl
fields.description: This is an incredible tea with a rich history that dates back over 1000 years. Fragrant jasmine blossoms are gently mixed with the most tender organic green tea leaves with silvery tips. They are hand rolled into small pearls that bloom in your glass.

fields.name: Green Snail Spring
fields.description: Pure “Bi Lo Chun" from China. Hand-picked and handrolled, this green has the most curious aroma and buttery smooth flavor. For centuries this style of Spring-pick tea has been considered one of China’s famous teas for its unique lightly sweet taste, unusual vegetal character and smooth cup.

fields.name: Wulu Mountain Mist
fields.description: Pure “Wulu" spring tea from China. Freshly handcrafted grown at high elevations among lush mountain tops and mist. This special grade first-pick tea creates a smooth and wonderfully mellow and butttery cup with a fresh sweet taste.

fields.name: Precious Eyebrows
fields.description: Pure “Chun Mee” from China. Perk up your own precious brows with a smooth brew bursting with brisk, vegetal flavor. Its leaves are hand-rolled into a coiled shape and produce a nice green cup with a plum-like aftertaste.

fields.name: Gunpowder Pearl
fields.description: Pure “Zhucha” or Pearl Tea from China. Get out the big guns with this roasted, slightly smoky tea that brews a rich, sweet flavor. Tightly-rolled leaves unfold when brewed, producing a strong and full golden brew. It's a big and bold bang for the buck.

fields.name: Dragonwell Superior
fields.description: Pure superior grade “Long Jing” DragonWell from Zhejiang China. Feed the beast with this smooth, elegant tea with buttery, vegetal flavor. One of China’s famous green teas for a darn good reason; this is premium, Spring picked, pan-fried tender leaves hand-crafted to be simply delicious.

fields.name: Precious Jade Dew
fields.description: Pure organic “Gyokuro” 2011 Harvest from Kyushu Japan. The best, young leaves from the finest plants are used to produce this special tea that brews a jade green color with a very sweet, creamy, taste. This premium tea undergoes a shade grown process that enhances the deep green color, flavor and antioxidant properties of each delicious cup. Gyokuro is considered Japan's finest tea and an organically grown Gyokuro of this quality is a rare thing. Indulge in green tea that is truly sublime.

fields.name: Premium Sencha
fields.description: Pure premium “Sencha” tea 2011 Harvest, Kyushu Japan. This steamed tea has a distinctive green leaf and brews a delicious cup with fresh, grassy aroma and smooth rich taste. This tea is produced to time honored precision crafted in the Aichi region of Japan famous for spectacular quality green teas.

fields.name: Brown Rice Tea
fields.description: Pure top grade organic “Genmaicha” from Japan. Green tea meets Rice Crispies in this favorite that is as rich in flavor as it is rich with history. A traditional blend of fine quality steamed Sencha green tea and toasted rice produce a warm brown rice aroma and fresh grassy taste. There's a lot of Genmaicha out there, we went for the 'good stuff'. No craggily leaf here. Just beautiful tender leaves and toasted kernels, produced to Japanese perfection. Sip, savor, enjoy — a great Genmaicha is a beautiful thing.

fields.name: Genmai Matcha
fields.description: Pure premium “Genmaicha Iri Matcha” from Japan. Brown rice tea is skillfully blended in Japan with “Matcha” fine ground green tea for a supercharged version of the classic bursting with extra greenness, full body and light sweetness. Matcha tea is loaded with many times the nutrients and flavor than any other green tea. Fine grade matcha is blended in Japan with steamed sencha and rice kernels for a cup that's a toasty roasty, clean and green Genmaicha Matcha experience.

fields.name: Green Twig
fields.description: Pure green “Kukicha” from Kyushu Japan. You’ll never look at sticks and stems the same again. An unusually awesome tea, this Japanese old school favorite made from the stems and leaves of green tea produces a creamy lightly sweet flavor.

fields.name: Roasted Twig
fields.description: Pure roasted “Kukicha” from Japan. Low caff and never bitter, you won't believe you're drinking green tea. Charcoal roasted to perfection, browned stems and leaf brew an amber cup with toasty, caramel-like flavor.

fields.name: Late Harvest
fields.description: Pure “Bancha” from Japan. Harvested late in the season from the green tea fields of Japan, you won’t mind running “late” yourself after sipping this green tea with large, pale leaves that brew a brisk, grassy cup with a sweet aroma.

fields.name: Fine Matcha 25g
fields.description: Pure finely ground organic green tea leaves from Japan. Matcha is one of the tea world's most unique teas. Whipped into intense frothy liquor, we call it the “espresso of green tea”. Matcha is creamy, oceanic and fragrant. It's potent. Real potent. It's a healthy boost for mind and body containing powerful vitamins and minerals. Matcha is the strongest and healthiest of any tea.

fields.name: Creme Brulee
fields.description: The French word for love is “amour” and this roasted oolong is love transformed. Amber oolong is infused with creamy notes of vanilla bean and herbs for a taste that’s smooth, lightly sweet and toasty with lovely lingering flavor. A blend of roasted oolong leaves, vanilla, roasted green tea and licorice.

fields.name: Jasmine Beauty
fields.description: Handcrafted oolong artfully blended to release delectable jasmine notes with a smooth, sweet taste. Rare tea leaves are harvested from ancient, wild Chinese tea trees up to 1700 years old. The full, smooth qualities of this oolong with the sweet fresh fragrance of real jasmine blossoms make this an uncommon jasmine treat.

fields.name: Ginger Pear Oolong
fields.description: Roasted oolong lightly kissed with the essences of fresh pear and spicy ginger. This sweet and spicy blend starts with Wuyi oolong grown high in the mountains of China then mixed with pear and ginger root for a lightly soft, fruity and toasty warm taste.

fields.name: Plumberry Oolong
fields.description: Close your eyes and imagine aromas of juicy plum tarts toasting near a roasting fire. Succulent tangy schizandra berries and darkened oolong tea is blended with the light essence of plum and hibiscus petals revealing a sweet, tangy and gentle brew.

fields.name: Silk and Citrus
fields.description: Slip into this smooth blend and say "hello sexy" to this special lemon zest vanilla kissed tea. Roasted oolong pouchong leaves are blended with natural vanilla, citrus and lemon myrtle for a creamy smooth, refreshingly warm, silky sweet treat.

fields.name: Peach Oolong
fields.description: Take a visit to the orchard, the flavor and aromas of fresh picked peaches amongst toasty oak swirl within this mountain grown Wuyi oolong. Grab your own bushel of hand blended oolong, rosehips, essences of apricot, peach and marigold petals.

fields.name: Jade Oz
fields.description: Osmanthus Flower "Gui Hua" Oolong from Taiwan. Light luxurious “Jade” oolong is infused with the floral aromas of osmanthus creating a luscious flavor that lifts the senses. Delicate, fruity and floral with lingering body and peach-like flavor, this classic blend of high mountain grown lightly oxidized oolong that has been crafted with the fragrant golden osmanthus blossoms in a time honored tradition.

fields.name: Mountain Orchid
fields.description: Pure, rare high mountain oolong from Taiwan. Special top grade leaves are lightly oxidized yielding natural lilac flavor unique to high mountain oolongs. Brewed multiple times, each infusion reveals distinctive flavor that's full, floral and outrageously good.

fields.name: Iron Goddess of Mercy
fields.description: Pure “Ti Kuan Yin” from Taiwan. Find the god or goddess in you with this classic that is a must-have in every oolong lover’s journey. Savor smooth, tangy and slight nutty notes with sweet floral flavor in a classic oolong of medium oxidation value.

fields.name: Iron Goddess Dark
fields.description: Pure “Ti Kuan Yin” from Taiwan. The "dark sister” of the original greener goddess, this tea is crafted with greater oxidization for a darker rich, woody aroma and full taste. Handrolled, hand roasted leaves make for a toasty tea with warm roasted character that can be resteeped over and over for multiple delights.

fields.name: Roasted Qilan
fields.description: Pure “Qilan” is a semi-oxidized Chinese oolong tea. Dark and toasty, smooth and smoky, our Qilan is crafted with big curly leaves to reveal a hearty flavor. With a full body that's super smooth, this amber brew is good on its own or paired with foods.

fields.name: Wuyi Rock
fields.description: Pure “Wuyi” is Chinese oolong tea of exceptional quality. Dark and toasty, smooth and lightly smoky, Wuyi's large leaves grown high in the mountains are crafted for rich, full flavor. Its amber brew is never bitter and always delightfully smooth.

fields.name: Purple Indo
fields.description: Pure heavily oxidized oolong from Indonesia. This aged rare oolong gets ooohs and ahhs from exotic tea hunters. 99% oxidized darkness produces rich toasty tea with purplish brews. Enjoy handrolled leaves unfurling with each smoky sweet infusion.

fields.name: Coconight
fields.description: Roasted coconut flavors soar from this smooth black tea. Dark, toasty and coconutty, this is a luscious blend of black tea, coconut, roasted green tea bits and cornflowers. It's smooth and might just soothe a craving for a taste of the exotic.

fields.name: Vanilla Sky
fields.description: You’ll be seeing stars with this velvety tea. Rich, full-bodied Assam black tea combined with natural soothing vanilla bits along with hand-tied star shaped white tea. This simple combo is, quite simply, a perfect vanilla black tea.

fields.name: Black Satin
fields.description: Curb those cravings for sweets with black tea that’s as smooth as silk. Black tea with cocoa mint notes in an artful blend of bold Assam tea with cacao nibs, mint, chocolate and vanilla essence for intoxicating aromas and smooth splendid flavor.

fields.name: Spiced Citrus
fields.description: Tea lovers rejoice for this classic citrus-spice combo. A flavor combination that has been around for generations, ours is blended to be smooth, zesty and delicious. Orange bits, assam tea and cinnamon chips soothe and stimulate the senses.

fields.name: House Chai
fields.description: Get your spice on with our organic house-chai that’s bound to please. Blended with tradition, this chai is created with a strong black Assam tea, cinnamon, dried ginger, cloves, cardamom and pieces of vanilla. A spicy bold tea with a classic chai kick.

fields.name: Chili Chai
fields.description: Not for the faint of heart, this chai packs a some serious heat. The hottest tea we've made (by demand) it's Assam tea, chili peppers, Theo™ dark chocolate (v), ginger, cinnamon, cloves, cardamom and vanilla. WARNING:Contains real chili heat.

fields.name: Black joy
fields.description: Walk with a skip in your step after sipping this blend that's lightly peppery and sweet. A stimulating blend designed to lift your senses and renew your stamina. Get joy from South Indian black tea leaves, coriander, cloves and marigold flower petals.

fields.name: Biscotti
fields.description: Fresh baked almond cookie aromas linger in this smooth black tea. Reminiscent of sweet scents straight from the kitchen, it's a comforting, tasty, warm and toasty mix of black tea, almond, cinnamon chips and safflower for a soothing almond delight.

fields.name: Coffeebreak
fields.description: Coffee kickers delight with a latte-like tea infused with toasty aromas and lingering coffee kissed taste. Black tea leaves are combined with real coffee beans, cocoa nibs, roasted tea, orange pieces and a touch of stevia leaf.

fields.name: Mango Basil
fields.description: It's off to the tropics with an island sweet taste and satin like smoothness in a full bodied tea. This intoxicating combination of black tea, sweet basil, mango bits, natural mango essence and calendula create a culinary twist on tropical tastes.

fields.name: Cherry Bomb
fields.description: Surrender to black tea bursting with fruity black cherry flavor. High grown Ceylon black teas are blended with flower blossoms, rosehips and natural organic cherry essences to create a flowery fruity cherry kissed infusion. Great

fields.name: Tiger Tail
fields.description: Tame that wild beast. Fresh bites of ginger contrast the smooth fruity sweetness of peach to have you purring from first to last sip. Indian Black tea, ginger, peach bits, natural essences and whole clove make black tea even peachier with a hint of spice.

fields.name: Black n Blue
fields.description: Say goodbye to the blues and hello to a bright cup with fresh blueberry taste. A blend of quality Ceylon black tea lightly fused with hibiscus petals, elderberries, currants and cornflowers for a delicious berry taste that's uplifting hot and refreshing on ice.

fields.name: Earl Grey Bouquet
fields.description: Earl Grey blended with lavender and jasmine, it’s “Lady Grey” taken to another level. Aromatic lavender and jasmine marry with citrusy bergamot black tea to uplift the senses and satisfy a craving for a fragrant, smooth and floral cup.

fields.name: Earl Grey Creme
fields.description: Classic Earl Grey black tea with a silky twist. Wildly popular hot or iced our Earl is fresh, citrus sweet with a vanilla finish. Ceylon black tea is blended with Sicilian bergamot, natural vanilla essences and blossoms for a delicious spin on the classic.

fields.name: Earl Grey Classic
fields.description: Classic Earl Grey that is blended with fine Ceylon and China teas with exceptionally bright aromas and taste. Natural essence from the aromatic skin of the bergamot fruit is used to flavor this traditional tea with a famously unique citrus taste.

fields.name: English Breakfast
fields.description: Classic “breakfast” blend of select Assam and Ceylon teas for those who like a strong tea to match a stiff upper lip. Full bodied, robust with floral notes, this blend is great on its own and splendid with milk and sweetener exuding soft aromas of honey.

fields.name: Irish Breakfast
fields.description: Classic “breakfast” tea blend of Assam teas. If you like your teas strong like your whiskey, then this tea is for you. It’s a robust, assertive black tea designed for milk and sweetener answering the need for a strong morning cup in a classic “Irish” way.

fields.name: Assam
fields.description: Pure "Assam" tea from India. Our bold leaf Assam features full body and malty sweet taste. A great FairTrade tea coming from prestigious Rembeng Estate. Our select Assam delivers a superb brew with wonderful aroma and rich sweet taste.

fields.name: Yunnan
fields.description: Pure “Yunnan” Dian Hong tea from China. Produced in one of the world's oldest tea growing regions, with little bitterness, this "Yunnan Red" (black) tea is earthy sweet and exceptionally smooth unique to quality Yunnan golden tipped tea.

fields.name: Keemun
fields.description: Pure “Keemun” from China is a world renowned Chinese tea with fruity aromas and smooth taste. It's known as Qimen in China's Anhui provence where it is grown, our Keemun produces an amber brew that's rich and smooth with light fruity notes.

fields.name: Darjeeling
fields.description: Pure “Darjeeling” from India. From the high elevation Selim Hill gardens of Darjeeling in West Bengal India, this tea is often referred to as the champagne of teas. This fine estate tea has a delicate flavor with light musky spiciness and a flowery fruity finish.

fields.name: Ceylon
fields.description: Pure “Ceylon Orange Pekoe” from Sri Lanka. This classic tea from the generations old tea growing region that was once called Ceylon. Classic flavor that’s full bodied, mellow and lightly sweet. There’s no “orange” in this tea, the name refers to the grade and style of the high quality leaf pick.

fields.name: Nilgiri
fields.description: Pure “Nilgiri” tea from India. A delicate and superb tea from a region known for the finest of black teas. This high-elevation Blue Mountain tea has colorful tipped leaves that produce a medium bodied brew that is fresh, aromatic, fragrant and flavorful.

fields.name: Vietnam
fields.description: Pure “Nam Lahn” Orange Pekoe from Vietnam. Wild-grown teas from ancient trees 700-800 years old grown in remote Western Vietnam have a distinctive rich, malty character and are known to have double the antioxidants of other black teas.

fields.name: Russian Caravan
fields.description: Pure “Russian Caravan” smoked tea. A blend of Yunnan teas and Lapsang Souchong. Bold, mellow and smoky, this is a blend popularized in old world Russia that’s rich, balanced and created for a less-intense pine smoked aroma and flavor.

fields.name: Pine Smoked, Lapsang
fields.description: Classic “Lapsang Souchong” from China. Can't have your tea by the campfire? Now you can bring that feeling home with this classic black tea traditionally smoked with pine providing an intensely smoky Scotch-like cup with curious campfire aroma.

fields.name: Cocoa Puerh
fields.description: Bold leaf, chocolatey pu-erh fuses the natural chocolate notes of the dark pu-erh with aromatic cocoa nibs for a rich, smooth, cocoa kissed brew. A great alternative to coffee, this is a custom blend of pu-erh, cocoa nibs and cocoa extract.

fields.name: Citra Pu-erh
fields.description: A centuries old pairing of citrus with earthy pu-erh in an updated way. A rich and intriguing blend of smooth bold-leaf pu-erh, orange pieces and lemongrass. Citrus promotes calming and the deep dark pu-erh can take you away.

fields.name: Pu-erh Soother
fields.description: Minty, earthy, bold and beautiful this tea brings together time honored digestives in one. A deep soothing brew that's doubles as a tummy tonic and hangover helper. Pu-erh, chrysanthemum and mint is blended for a rich, cooling bold pu-erh taste.

fields.name: Chai Pu-erh
fields.description: A spiced pu-erh blend that is superbly designed to warm and invigorate the senses. Soothing, spicy, dark and dank this blend of bold leaf pu-erh, ginger root, cinnamon chips and whole clove brew a hearty cup with rich spiced pu-erh taste.

fields.name: Ancient Tree Dark
fields.description: Pure loose leaf "shou" pu-erh from Yunnan China. Broad tea leaves from old growth forest tea “trees” are prepared in the darkened shou style resulting in a brew that’s smooth, earthy and lightly smoky. Not too bold, not too light, it’s just right.

fields.name: Yunnan Bold Leaf
fields.description: Pure loose leaf "shou" pu-erh from Yunnan China. Deep, inky and earthy, this is a pu-erh for those that like it bold. Made in the darkened shou style, the tea brews deep amber color and stirs up woodsy aromas of fresh tilled soil and leather.

fields.name: Mini Bowls Cooked
fields.description: Pure cooked “shou tuocha” pu-erh from Yunnan China. These wee little bowls of compressed tea have full-bodied earthy flavor. Little nuggets of pu-erh goodness can be infused many times revealing smooth mellow flavor. While these little bowls are cute as a button they deliver dark bold flavor with deep earthiness like no other.

fields.name: Mini Bowls Raw
fields.description: Pure green “sheng tuocha” pu-erh from Yunnan China. Itty bitty compressed tea bowls will have you singing like a bird for a unique brew that is slightly smoky, brisk, vegetal, raw style pu-erh. Green tea-like bowls of fermented raw pu-erh are very invigorating and can be resteeped a multitude of times.

fields.name: Mountain Brick Raw
fields.description: Pure 2003 "sheng" compressed pu-erh from China, this flowery tea comes from ancient tea plants high in the Jing Mai Mountains. Large leaves prepared in the raw pu-erh style brews a honey-like, delightful greener bittersweet taste. It's pure stone mold pressed ancient strain pu-erh leaf. Provided to you loose leaf from compressed bricks.

fields.name: Wild Arbor Cake Raw
fields.description: Pure 2004 "sheng bing" pu-erh from Yunnan, China. Stone pressed ancient strain tea leaf infuses to create a musky sweet cup with hints of apricot and honey. Medium dark in its oxidization, it's old world style pu-erh that can be resteeped multiple times for a smooth mellow taste. Provided to you loose leaf from the compressed cake.

fields.name: Ancient Tree Raw
fields.description: Pure handrolled and roasted "sheng" pu-erh from China. A luxurious tea harvested from ancient tea trees in the old growth forests of China. Tribes continue to harvest this tea from ancient trees as their ancestors did centuries ago. The leaves from tea trees planted over 1000 years ago for a brisk, energizing delicious cup with honey-like taste.

fields.name: Cocoluxe
fields.description: Indulge in this luxurious sweet coconut creation that is both nutritious and delicious. Savor this exotic mix of rooibos tea with coconut shreds, cacao nibs, cinnamon, star anise, rose and sweetleaf for an intoxicating coconut kissed full sensory lift.

fields.name: Red Hot
fields.description: Cinnamon red hot rooibos for those who like it spicy sweet. Add some fire to your belly with this addictive blend of rooibos tea blended with cinnamon chips, chili peppers and stevia leaf created to be cinnamon sweet, healthful with a touch of heat.

fields.name: Red Satin
fields.description: Curb those cravings with a cocoa mint rooibos that is as smooth as silk. This lightly sweet and sultry creation of healthy rooibos tea blended with cacao nibs, peppermint leaf, honeybush and vanilla transforms rooibos into a soothing decadent treat.

fields.name: Chai Rooibos
fields.description: Add spice to your day or night with this herbal chai that can be enjoyed anytime. This tea-free, caffeine-free rooibos chai is a healthy blend that's lightly fruity, mildly spicy take on traditional chai taste with rooibos, cinnamon, ginger, clove and cardamom.

fields.name: Floraberry
fields.description: Rolling fields of flowers and berries are conjured up in this flavorful tea that's fused with a floral fruity bouquet. Berry sweet with hints of lavender, this popular tea is a soothing and refreshing blend of rooibos, lavender, rose, currants and elderberries.

fields.name: Calypso
fields.description: Mango scented ocean breezes are conjoured up in a lightly sweet tropical cup designed to give a healthy boost and transport the tastebuds with sun-dried green rooibos, mango pieces, apple bits, calendula, orange peel and rose petals.

fields.name: Cherry Amaretto
fields.description: It is love at first scent with this fresh and seductive rooibos tea. Swoon for almond sweet rooibos that is blended to please with organic cherry, rosehips, natural almond essences and almond slivers for a healthful, soothing cherry almond treat.

fields.name: Coconut Lav
fields.description: Rooibos and coconut blended with uplifting lavender is a simply to-die-for combo — try it you’ll see. The earthy richness of coconut rooibos enhanced by the sweet aromas of lavender transforms rooibos into a succulent aromatic cup.

fields.name: Ginger Lime
fields.description: Refresh with green rooibos kissed with lemon lime taste. Green rooibos is the same as red rooibos only unfermented for grassy healthy taste. Rooibos is blended with ginger, lime leaves, lemongrass, lemon myrtle and citrus bits for a fresh bright flavor.

fields.name: Capetown
fields.description: Calming yet rejuvenating, this combo is a floral potpourri of a creation. With sweet, citrus, floral and minty flavor this tea bursts with cheer. Restore with rooibos crafted with chamomile, mint, rose, orange and lemon verbena for a refreshing soother.

fields.name: Red Earl
fields.description: The classic Earl is red all over in this caffeine free herbal blend of the Earl Grey tea. Fine bergamot essence is blended with pure rooibos for a perfect amber colored brew with bold citrus notes so you can enjoy the flavor of Earl Grey without the kick.

fields.name: Red Peach
fields.description: Here’s to long life, as peaches have long been considered a symbol of long life and immortality. Good hot and refreshing over ice, healthy antioxidant rich rooibos tea is blended with natural peach essences and calendula for life a little more peachy.

fields.name: Rooibos Pure
fields.description: Pure rooibos has smooth rich earthy full flavor with hints of vanilla nuttiness. It's a nutritional powerhouse loaded with nutrients, antioxidants, vitamins and minerals but all the hoopla is just as much about its soothing, refreshing and unique taste.

fields.name: Coconut Yerba
fields.description: Argentinean yerba meets toasty coconut

fields.name: Mate Tropic
fields.description: Sail away with Yerba touched with a taste of the tropics in this mango-passion infused concoction crafted to lift the spirits. Fruits and uplifting yerba mate are blended with calendula and hibiscus petals to brighten any season rain or shine.

fields.name: Chai Mate
fields.description: The miracle of mate meets the spiciness of chai head on for a stimulating herbal twist on the traditional chai.  Rich with spices, roots and herbs, this flavorful blend contains yerba maté, cardamom, cloves and cinnamon to uplift your senses.

fields.name: Citra Mate
fields.description: Zesty mate makes good with a blend that crafted to refresh and stimulate. Great for a work day or workout, fresh green yerba mate leaf is blended with lemongrass, orange peel and lemon myrtle making for an aromatic energizing citrus kissed tonic.

fields.name: Mint Mate
fields.description: Yerba mate has gone minty in this refreshing mate with crisp aroma and soothing flavor of powerful mint tea. Green yerba mate is blended with spearmint, peppermint leaves and a touch of stevia leaf for stimulating mentholated liquid energy.

fields.name: Cocoa Mate
fields.description: Go koo-koo for cocoa with this toasty twist on Mate. This yerba mate's roasted brown leaf brews a toasted cup with a light chocolate taste. Roasted yerba mate, cacao nibs, carob and floral petals make for a cocoa kissed earthy mate tea.

fields.name: Java Mate
fields.description: Yerba Mate is a go-to brew for folks kicking coffee. This blend of roasted yerba mate, carob and ramon nut creates an earthy, dark roasted richness that can help satisfy a coffee craving. Try cream and sweetener to with this tea.

fields.name: Green Yerba, Brazil
fields.description: Pure “Yerba Mate” from Paraña Brazil. There's mate, and then there's mate. This is exceptional grade fresh green yerba mate that is fresh-packaged shortly after picking, not aged, for a fresher greener taste. It’s crafted with only the leaves of mate and has a green finish, bursting with minerals and vitamins —it is clean, green and high octane.

fields.name: Aged Yerba, Arg.
fields.description: Pure “Yerba Mate” from Argentina. Yerba from this region is enjoyed by millions and is the most predominant yerba mate style out there. Different from “fresh packed ”Brazilian Green, this is aged and dried in traditional Argentenian style to bring out a complex, distinctive smooth and lightly spiced flavor.

fields.name: Dark Roast Yerba
fields.description: Pure Dark Roast “Yerba Mate” from Argentina. Beautiful dark roasted leaves of yerba mate brew a tea with a toasty, nutty, coffee-like flavor and aroma. Fresh green yerba mate leaf is roasted exactly like coffee in modified coffee roasters making it dark in appearance with a rich, roasted, caramel-like flavor.

fields.name: Tranquility
fields.description: Chill. Feeling the need to relax? Drift away to a serene place with a perfectly tranquil blend that brews a sweet, floral and cooling taste. Delicious and soothing, this artful blend of chamomile, mint, and rooibos is designed to give a little peace.

fields.name: Melody
fields.description: Peace and inspiration are in perfect tune with this comforting chamomile citrus creation. An excellent chillout tea, this is a mellow yellow mix of soothing chamomile, uplifting citrus and petals of hibiscus to help keep you in perfect pitch.

fields.name: Ginger Zest
fields.description: Meet the real fresh maker. This crisp invigorating blend has pep with a touch of lemon ginger vigor. Soothing hot and refreshing over ice, this is a smooth blend of lemongrass, ginger root, honeybush and lemon verbena that's a rejuvenating delight.

fields.name: Shaman
fields.description: Find your "ooohm" state with this revitalizing blend of Tulsi herb “the elixir of life" and refreshing, fortifying spices designed to bring peacefulness into your day. Tulsi leaves, fennel seeds, orange peel and mint brew an elixir that is lightly citrus spiced.

fields.name: Serenity
fields.description: Holy Basil Tulsi blended with rose petals and soothing herbs for a floral sweet botanical infusion. Lift your senses and satisfy your taste buds with this blend of Tulsi, rose petals, lemon myrtle, chamomile, coconut shreds and stevia leaf.

fields.name: Mind Body Soul
fields.description: Cool out with a sweet fresh blend of select botanicals used to sharpen the mind and replenish the body. Based on ayurvedic tradition this tonic is crafted to aid digestion and memory with a calming blend of ginkgo leaf, licorice, coriander, fennel and mint.

fields.name: Tropical Cocktail
fields.description: You always were a little “fruity”. Why not go all the way with a blend with fruity finish and tropical aromas. Hot or iced, this sweet, tart blend of hibiscus, rosehips, black currants, rooibos, orange peel and mango brews refreshment that's fruity and bright.

fields.name: Sherbet
fields.description: Reminiscent of citrusy sherbet on a hot summer day, this is a light and bright blend that is loaded with vitamin C and fresh cheery, sweet flavor. Contains rose hips, hibiscus petals, orange peel, apple pieces, and pineapple with fruit-punch taste.

fields.name: Cranapple
fields.description: Autumn is here anytime with this fruity brew with the crisp warm flavor of baked apples and cranberry. Soothing hot and refreshing over ice, this sweet tart blend of dried apple, hibiscus, rosehips and cranberry essences reveal a fresh pink cup.

fields.name: Fire and Ice
fields.description: Feeling hot under the collar? Take a deep breath and cool those jets with a soothing blend of hibiscus flowers, rose petals, chamomile flowers and peppermint that's fresh and comforting. Fruity, flowery and lightly minty this tea brews a little bit of serenity.

fields.name: Currant Berry
fields.description: This tooti-frooti blend brews purple-pink infusions with sweet-tart taste and vitamin C punch. A bright mix of fruit, flowers and bursting berry. A blend of black currants, red currants, hibiscus, elderberries and rosehips for a brew that is sweet and refreshing.

fields.name: Sugarplum
fields.description: Plum kissed cinnamon spiced herbal tea that excites the senses. A blend of cinnamon chips, ginger, hibiscus petals and plum bursting with vitaminC. It's fruity warming aromas with fruit spice flavor makes for the perfect seasonal treat.

fields.name: Immunity
fields.description: A flu fighter immunity booster that brews a tangy, sweet cup. Load-up on vitamin C, support your immune system and relieve stress on your body with a blend of enchinacea, hibiscus, rosehips, tulsi, currants, licorice and lavender.

fields.name: Stressless
fields.description: Relax and restore with a floral cup designed for liquid relaxation. Lightly sweet and super soothing, this brew is blend of chamomile, lavender, lemongrass, hibiscus petals, licorice, rooibos and calendula designed to help unwind.

fields.name: Cleanse
fields.description: Gentle, clean and soothing, this tea is designed as a general detoxification tea with lemony minty taste with sweet lingering flavor. Cleansing lemongrass and dandelion leaf with peppermint, licorice concoction are blended to delight.

fields.name: WonderWoman
fields.description: This blend uses ago old ingredients to help keep you in perfect tune. This minty sweet creation combines soothing nettle, raspberry leaf, peppermint leaf, chamomile flowers, ginger root, dandelion leaf, oatstraw, horsetail, stevia and rose to help keep you in balance.

fields.name: SuperMan
fields.description: Designed to promote men’s health using time honored herbs and botanicals, this blend is an earthy blend of roots and berries. Burdock, dandelion, marshmallow, nettle and eleuthero roots, hawthorn berries, saw palmetto berry, fennel and oatstraw to aid in prostate and general health.

fields.name: Licorice Fix
fields.description: Licorice lovers delight over this sweet licorice root spiced tea. This blend will satisfy your sweet-tooth with a earthy sweet blend of licorice root, orange peel, cinnamon, ginger and fennel that coats the throat with powerful licorice healing.

fields.name: Aphroditea
fields.description: Sparks fly with this intoxicating aphrodisiac with potent herbs used for lovin' over the ages. Get tipsy with this spicy blend of damiana, gotu kola, kava kava, saw palmetto, cinnamon, ginger, clove, licorice, cardamom and rose.

fields.name: Chamomile Flowers
fields.description: Calm yourself from inside out with sweet mellow whole organic chamomile blossoms that can helps ease mind and body. Fresh and beautiful dried flowers brew a golden cup with a flowery apple like taste that is superbly calming, cleansing and soothing.

fields.name: Lavender Blossoms
fields.description: If only the world was paved in lavender. A tonic for mind and body, it can soothe the spirit, calm the nerves and relieve stress. Lavender is soft, lightly sweet, intensely aromatic and with a pale purple color that tastes exquisite with a drop of honey.

fields.name: Peppermint Leaves
fields.description: Add some pep day or night with Pacific Northwest grown peppermint leaf that deeply soothes and refreshes. Known as a powerful digestive tonic for unsettled tummies, our peppermint is top grade leaf with intense clean tingly mint flavor like no other.

fields.name: Lemongrass
fields.description: Exquisite tea that's simple and soothing, our pure lemongrass is cooling, clear and crisp with a distinctive, lemony aroma and taste. Known to relieve fatigue and stress, soothe the stomach and help with sleep, we love it for its clean citrus fresh taste.

fields.name: Licorice Root
fields.description: Sweet and full flavored, not at all the taste of licorice the candy, this root has been brewing relief for centuries. It's known to soothe a sore throat, aid a cold and the tummy too, it's good for oral health and creates a uniquely rooty sweet fragrant brew.

fields.name: Ginger Root
fields.description: Ginger root brews a fiery liquor with spicy sweet taste. One of the planet's most widely used remedies, it's cold relieving, stomach soothing and can lift the senses. Delish on its own or with a honey lemon twist, its soothing heat packs a spicy kick.

fields.name: Hibiscus Petals
fields.description: Brilliant red and rich with tangy fruity taste, hibiscus tea is made from pure hibiscus petals and nothing else. Deep, strong, sweet and tart, the infusion of this flower packs a full flavor punch that’s vitamin C charged fresh and fruity delight.

fields.name: Tulsi Herb
fields.description: "Holy basil" Tulsi from India is an ancient medicinal herb used for 5000 years said to reduce the effects of daily stress and aging, enhances calm and clarity, boosts immunity and stamina and is antiox rich with a soothing citrusy clove taste. Ours is a blend of 3 types of tulsi, Rama, Krisha and Vana Tulsi, in a time honored healthful brew.
